{"tid":1507067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】實試舉報Facebook假新聞1日內有成效 「曱甴論」屬第一級仇恨言論","createTime":"2019-08-26T04:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:42:30.000Z","uid":54373,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd2b53721a54576b6cfe2d2c98320de1cf31b3f","tid":1507067,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"建立時間 (HKT): 0826 06:00<br />\nTwitter、Facebook、YouTube相繼出手刪除假新聞假賬戶，fake news剷不盡，網軍吹又生。如果網民見到自己舉報又可不可行得通？Gadget Guy實試過，在Facebook舉報欺凌國泰員工的帖子，1個鐘頭多點收到審查結果指，移除了相關帖子和相片，莫以善小而不為，舉報fake news人人有責。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舉報有分舉報帖子或舉報專頁，大致上做法都是按下「尋求支援或舉報帖子」，之後再選擇理由，記得還要在之後再按多次「舉報帖子／專頁」才算完成舉報。舉報過的個案可在「支援收件匣」中看到進度（ <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/support/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsupport%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY0WuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=cd95e2a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/support/</a> ）。<br />\n<br />\n關於舉報機制，Facebook自己有公佈一些社群守則，記者個人細閱之後覺得Facebook對「不實報道」容忍度較高，在守則中指出很難區分嘲諷和不實，並且明說「不會移除 Facebook 上的不實報道」，只會降低其散播率。<br />\n<br />\n反而仇恨言論的描述比較嚴謹和詳盡，分了三大級別，當中第1級重中之重就是「磨滅人性的言論」，例如特定非人化的比喻，包括昆蟲，正正貼合了警察常說的曱甴論。而「起底」一類的帖子，也可以舉報為「欺凌」內容。<br />\n<br />\n從經驗得知要舉報整個專頁、群組或賬戶，需要有大量及連續內容涉及違規，一些開得比較久的專頁亦較難舉報至關閉，但不代表舉報沒有用。連續成功舉報會不斷增加個人賬戶禁言時間，如大導演李力持先生曾被禁言30天。<br />\n<br />\n最後提提大家Facebook舉報過程絕對保密，所以如見到助長歪風的違規內容，不要猶豫，馬上檢舉。<br />\n<br />\n記者：司徒港燊<br />\n編輯：鄒仲安"},{"pid":"015d0b9e13151589c6b8b2ed006e7c09caa09f26","tid":1507067,"uid":231102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:23:19.000Z","msg":"可能大家會覺得唔啱聽，<br />\n不過我諗我地都唔好再叫黑警做狗，<br />\n一來有機會同樣被視作仇恨言論，<br />\n二來混淆真正嘅警犬，<br />\n三來侮辱人類最忠實嘅朋友，<br />\n四來絕對有更適合嘅替代詞：<strong>GESTAPO</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港警察，蓋世太保</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n參考：<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/蓋世太保\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E8%93%8B%E4%B8%96%E5%A4%AA%E4%BF%9D&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY0WuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=f028fea3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/蓋世太保</a>"},{"pid":"8404ae2c62da4f3dadf4da05b2aad810542f9033","tid":1507067,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:24:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd9c709244a7cedd00883d50a28cef55600f3e15","tid":1507067,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},{"pid":"2a0cb2c266078fc81015f196d5ec5cd262ca977e","tid":1507067,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9083ce34b65a5747e0e1f6f6e4722582f6f1b7a4","tid":1507067,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:35:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44a54b0213117030af00624c800761b1c53fdc24","tid":1507067,"uid":300592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:40:39.000Z","msg":"Gestapopo <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715aad14b39a15b61263279ccd23059f363f7460","tid":1507067,"uid":153341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}